latestIgtvVideos.title: multimoves
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
animal movements 
1 lateral ape
2 Spider walk
3 Horse walk
4 Duck walk
5 Baboon walk
6 Bunny hops
7 Scorpion
8 Crab walk
9 Bear crawl
10 Reaching crab

you have to perform each exercise for 45 sec. and rest in between each set 15 sec. 
total circuits 4/5 
after each circuit  2 min of break.

note- if anyone have any shoulder pathology (dislocation, tennis elbow, Rotator cuff injury etc) then avoid this exercises.

latestPosts.caption:
🔺📢 Feedback 🔺📢
Dr. Ruchi Mittal, we started working out together online, it’s been 10 months.
It’s very good to see Doctor like her, 
NO Offence but so many doctors says women Should not lift heavy weights or should not follow No-carb diet but it is actually necessary.
As a doctor Ruchi always suggested everyone to avoid the direct intake of sugar even in her Own diet, she haven’t eat sugar since 10 months…
I feel very happy to train her because there was no day when I have to tell her to follow diet. she always been there very supportive and even we went through Shoulder injury but in that case also she haven’t skipped her meals or workout
 Thank you Ruchi ♥️
